data.description:
SELLER OFFERING 2-1 BUY DOWN WITH SELECT LENDER!
Freshly painted featuring wood-like tile, new carpet, 6 in. baseboards and 8 ft doors. Primary BR has custom floating shelves, 10K custom closet and upgraded fixtures. Chef's dream the kitchen with under cabinet lighting, custom 6K pantry, upgraded granite, convection oven, gas cooktop and new hardware. A second BR down is perfect for guests. Study has beveled French doors. Upstairs has 2 additional bedrooms, a game rm and a bonus rm that could easily be a media rm! Relax and unwind in your 30K outdoor oasis with 365 Synthetic Pet Turf Plus with T-cool temperature regulating infill and beautiful flower beds and landscaping. Jellyfish security lighting, solar lit gazebo, sitting area and graveled side yards with French drains make for a low maintenance yard. But don't forget about the garage which has a new garage door with interchangeable hardware and an epoxy coated floor! Tankless water heater and radiant barrier too! Ring security.
